title: Country Joe And The Fish - Electric Music For The Mind And Body
description:
Country Joe And The Fish - Electric Music For The Mind And Body 1967

One of the first psychedelic albums to come out of San Francisco


1. Flying High" (Joe McDonald)
2. Not So Sweet Martha Lorraine" (McDonald)
3. Death Sound Blues" (McDonald)
4. Happiness Is a Porpoise Mouth" (McDonald)
5. Section 43" (McDonald)
6. Superbird" (McDonald)
7. Sad and Lonely Times" (McDonald)
8. Love" (McDonald, Melton, Cohen, Barthol, Gunning, Hirsh)
9. Bass Strings" (McDonald)
10. The Masked Marauder" (McDonald)
11. Grace" (McDonald)

Musicians
Country Joe McDonald -- vocals, guitar, bells, tambourine
Barry Melton -- vocals, guitar
David Cohen -- guitar, organ
Bruce Barthol -- bass, harmonica
Gary "Chicken" Hirsh -- drums
